CLAUDE.md

# Composer-managed deps are installed per-environment via `composer install`.
# CI (.github/workflows/build.yml) runs `composer install --no-dev` before
# zipping a release, so vendor/ is rebuilt fresh for the artifact users see.
#
# Exception: vendor/Aws3/ is the php-scoper output for our vendor-prefixed
# AWS SDK. Regenerating it requires a php-scoper build step that isn't in
# CI today, so we keep it committed.
/vendor/*
!/vendor/Aws3/

# PHPUnit cache (generated per local run).
/.phpunit.cache/

# Playwright E2E artifacts.
/test-results/
/playwright-report/
/blob-report/
/playwright/.cache/
/tests/e2e/.auth/

# wp-env state (Docker volumes, generated config).
/.wp-env/